    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nWSL2, when entering Neovim, cursor changes from vertical line to block, but does not restore to vertical line cursor after exiting Neovim.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim\nZZ\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nCursor shape restored to be vertical line after exiting nvim.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNvim v0.13.0-dev-468+g2dc0efccb0 commit 2dc0efccb0 & Nvim v0.12.2\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno, Vim 8.2.2121\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nWindows 11 25H2, WSL 2.7.3.0, WSL Ubuntu 22.04.5 LTS\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nWindows Terminal 1.24.10921.0\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nNvim v0.13.0-dev-468+g2dc0efccb0 commit 2dc0efccb0: build from GitHub repo (the master) & Nvim v0.12.2: GitHub release",
